quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  62,9,"O you who have faith! When the call is made for prayer on Friday, hurry toward the remembrance of Allah, and leave all business. That is better for you, should you know"
  62,10,"And when the prayer is finished disperse through the land and seek Allah’s grace, and remember Allah much so that you may be felicitous"
  62,11,"When they sight a deal or a diversion, they scatter off towards it and leave you standing! Say, ‘What is with Allah is better than diversion and dealing, and Allah is the best of providers.’"